    User gustafer
    ForwardX11 yes
    ForwardAgent yes
    UserKnownHostsFile /dev/null
    StrictHostKeyChecking no

##  (port forward for virtual-box)
Host localhost
    ForwardX11 yes
    ForwardAgent yes
    UserKnownHostsFile /dev/null
    StrictHostKeyChecking no

